"documents</b>—to collect specific information exactly where it's needed "
"within the template."
msgstr ""
"這樣，你便可新增自訂欄位，例如<b>文字區域、圖片、文件</b>等，以便在範本中的適"
"當位置，準確收集所需資訊。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This module helps you manage every step of the process, from initial "
"customer relationships to event planning and execution. With it, you can "
"effortlessly prepare and validate events, purchase the necessary raw "
"materials, and\n"
"            efficiently track your entire operation."
msgstr ""
"此模組可協助你管理工作流程的每個步驟，由最初建立客戶關係，以至其後的活動規劃"
"及執行。借助此模組，你可輕鬆為活動準備及進行驗證、採購所需的原材料及用品，\n"
"            高效追蹤所有營運工序。"

#. module: catering
#: model:product.template,description_sale:catering.product_product_127_product_template
msgid ""
"This package includes a dedicated wait staff positioned behind the bar for "
"the entire duration of the event. Please note, this service does not cover "
"table service after the dessert course.\n"
"\n"
"The package includes:\n"
"\n"
"- Soft drinks and sodas\n"
"- Still and sparkling water\n"
"- Red and White Wine\n"
"- Beers\n"
"\n"
"The predefined price package is calculated based on an allowance of 5 non-"
"alcoholic and 5 alcoholic drinks per guest. Any drinks consumed above this "
"allowance will be itemized and charged separately after the event."
msgstr ""
"此服務套餐會提供一位專屬服務員，在活動期間全程駐守吧台，為你服務。請留意，此"
"服務不包括甜品上菜後的餐桌服務。\n"
"\n"
"套餐提供：\n"
"\n"
"- 汽水、軟性飲品\n"
"- 普通飲用水、氣泡水\n"
"- 紅白葡萄酒\n"
"- 啤酒\n"
"\n"
"套餐預設價格按每位賓客 5 杯非酒精飲品及 5 杯酒精飲品的限額計算。任何超出限額"
"的飲品消耗，將在活動結束後詳列在賬單上，另行收取費用。"

