#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome to the <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Odoo Catering package."
"</font></strong>"
msgstr ""

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When you're ready, you have the flexibility to create an invoice for either "
"a full or a partial payment, such as a down payment. All invoices generated "
"are tracked and can be managed through the <b>Invoices app</b>."
msgstr ""
"完成設置後，你可隨時靈活開立發票，接受全額付款或先收取部份款項，例如訂金或首"
"期付款。系統會追蹤所有產生的發票，你亦可透過<b>發票應用程式</b>管理發票。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr "想與我們討論如何設定你的 Odoo 配置，甚至想探索更多？"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr "你可在主要 Dashboard 上，存取 Odoo 資料庫內所有已安裝的應用程式。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access the <b>Planning tool</b> via a button in the <b>top bar</b> "
"of the Project app. This tool allows you to <b>efficiently prepare and "
"schedule</b> the necessary workers for your event. Simply\n"
"            <b>select the desired shift</b> on the corresponding dates to "
"create it."
msgstr ""
"你可透過專案管理應用程式的<b>頂部列</b>按鈕，使用<b>工作規劃工具</b>。此工具"
"可協助你<b>高效預備及安排人手</b>，為活動配置所需工作人員。只需\n"
"            在相應日期上<b>選擇所需輪班</b>，即可輕易建立。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can also use a contact's email to automatically create an opportunity in "
"your CRM pipeline."
msgstr "你也可利用聯絡人的電郵地址，讓系統在客戶關係管道中，自動建立商機。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily invoice clients directly from a <b>Sales Order</b>. Each "
"order allows you to set specific <b>payment terms and conditions</b> "
"tailored to that client or project."
msgstr ""
"你可直接在<b>銷售單</b>內，向客戶開立發票。訂單可個別設定指定的<b>付款條款及"
"條件</b>，以切合目標客戶或相關專案的需要。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can easily tailor your website to provide the information you want for "
"potential leads. When a client contacts you through the contact page, their "
"submission will automatically create a new opportunity in your CRM pipeline."
msgstr ""
"你可輕鬆調整網站的功能及設計，向潛在客戶提供所需資料。客戶透過聯絡頁面聯絡你"
"時，他們提交表單的操作，會同時自動在你的客戶關係管理（CRM）管道中，建立一個新"
"的銷售機會。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade your Catering package and select the relevant checkbox"
msgstr ""
"還未匯入模擬數據？現在仍可執行此操作。請前往應用程式 &gt; 行業 &gt; 升級你的"
"「餐飲服務」套裝，然後選取相關勾選方格。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You need to duplicate several times the same shift? Press Ctrl and move the "
"shift, it will duplicate it automatically."
msgstr "需要多次複製同一個輪班？按住 Ctrl 鍵並拖曳輪班，便可自動複製。"

#. module: catering
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:catering.homepage
msgid ""
"Your catering service, transforming every occasion, from intimate dinners to "
"grand corporate events and fairytale weddings,&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"屬於你的餐飲服務，讓每個場合都煥然一新，不論是溫馨的晚餐聚會，到盛大的企業活"
"動，以至童話般的夢幻婚禮，"

